Annolid attribution:

This project was heavily inspired by Annolid, an annotation and instance
segmentation-based multiple animal tracking and behavior analysis package:

https://github.com/cplab/annolid
https://annolid.com/

Annolid is copyright (c) 2024 Computational Physiology Laboratory and is
distributed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0
International License.

This project was made because I could not figure out how to get Annolid working
for my workflow, but Annolid's methods were clear enough to guide a smaller,
focused implementation for SAM-based measurement.

This project is not affiliated with, sponsored by, or endorsed by Annolid or the
Computational Physiology Laboratory. Any changes, simplifications, omissions, or
